data.description: This Riverdale Single Story Home Available in April * Main Floor Features include: wood floors, vaulted ceilings, open livingroom, Spacious kitchen with dining room, master bedroom suite with private bath, bedroom 2 and 3; 2nd bathroom, & laundry room with washer and dryer. Basement features and family/rec room, bedroom 4, utility room, and storage rooms. Home back yard features a private deck, back patio, garden beds, and views of the mountains.For a full list of our available properties, please go to Available in April * $1,950/Rent * $1,950 Deposit * $50 Application Fee * NON Smoking * Pets Considered * Renter's Insurance Included.
